Package: patientSimPrepare
Type: Package
Title: Prepare Training/Test/Validation Datasets for patientSim ModelBundles
Version: 1.3.0
Author: Jarrod Dalton [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jarrod Dalton <daltonj@ccf.org>
Authors@R: person(given = "Jarrod",
                  family = "Dalton",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  email = "daltonj@ccf.org")
Description: Utilities to translate observational event and measurement tables, aligned to a patientSimCore schema,
    into reproducible training/test/validation datasets for one-step event and state transition models intended
    for use inside patientSim ModelBundles. This package is intentionally spec-first and schema-aligned.
License: Proprietary
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    stats,
    utils,
    patientSimCore (>= 1.2.5)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    digest,
    jsonlite,
    qs,
    arrow
